{"tid":1743183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五個月啦，大家好似唔記得咩叫「兄弟爬山，各有各做」","createTime":"2019-11-21T05:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:46:41.000Z","uid":237893,"like":63,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"579f6f670d167f9e26f45702f8c1becc948a892f","tid":1743183,"uid":237893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"今日好撚多分化撚<br />\n<br />\n投票又話港豬<br />\n唔投票又話港豬<br />\n塞地鐵又話失民意<br />\n又話只係要塞中環乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五個月啦，大家好似唔記得咩叫「兄弟爬山，各有各做」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我個人意見：<br />\n1. 區選一定要贏，所以票一定要投。放棄自己手上一票，咁我地爭取雙普選黎做乜鳩?<br />\n2. 黎明行動照做，民意已經歸晒邊，唔使再驚失民意！就好似今日CCTVB訪問果個人咁講：「佢地唔塞，地鐵都成日壞架啦」<br />\n3. 重建連儂牆<br />\n4. 重啟文宣機器<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目標一致，兄弟爬山，各有各做！<br />\n分化撚我屌你老母！"},{"pid":"b5e04a65952da4f7fb4331d6625d6d77fe0acf8f","tid":1743183,"uid":237893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:53:50.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"da325f1636cbc5ad17cce9e5afa8cd9c036bc3c8","tid":1743183,"uid":45028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"幫推 講得幾好"},{"pid":"01aa72c58a6b568c865b1ebf107eb99dd5c6377d","tid":1743183,"uid":185999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:54:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1398d3a3a3191317b45a68cf41714ec395df09","tid":1743183,"uid":323228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: maroon;\">要贏呀，其實可唔可以整翻幾日</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><strong>全民文宣日</strong></ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即係全力全世界一齊同一日打鍵盤文宣戰包括FB，IG，Air drop，同安全情況下快的整翻好的牆？呢度開PO集中比出文宣材料<br />\n其實周圍都可以係連農牆。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日選舉前集中文宣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>要贏呀！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7840a1f827e8663b42f384c0c6b16eeff808d16f","tid":1743183,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c58b6bdd017f4c4fcd5bd14fe010c1c036bc861","tid":1743183,"uid":169079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"各有各做，做到就做，咩都要做"},{"pid":"cb8b6a206aac8b304d829e97fe8d26e0f8964bed","tid":1743183,"uid":324877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"四個月就唔記得 你哋全部金魚黎架？無post嘅？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743187</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"723720efe11205f1e76e54b15be30aeac0f054e4","tid":1743183,"uid":51798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752da626be6670e66b0057f5bd4f89f13a9e3832","tid":1743183,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T05:58:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/f