提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=3fd2c198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=47dbeaef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=58154e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameM%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=5bd06b0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"7a22faccbc36a19b0e56257556394162815f76b2","tid":1743183,"uid":237893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:12:31.000Z","msg":"分化完未?"},{"pid":"99f61dcbe6fc3b1ced9d466234ca6b0171335093","tid":1743183,"uid":100371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5927bf9001992db2c4be292b9bde2c2751d414fc","tid":1743183,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:16:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{